  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "chapterTitle": "十八",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23303571_21_7274-7373",
          "range": "7274-7373",
          "rangeStart": 7274,
          "rangeEnd": 7373,
          "markText": "雨下给富人，也下给穷人；下给义人，也下给不义的人。其实，雨并不公道，因为下落在一个没有公道的世界上。\n祥子病了。大杂院里的病人并不止于他一个。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1731206909,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-11-10 10:48:29",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7274&rangeEnd=7373",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7274&rangeEnd=7373"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "一",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23303571_4_8284-8464",
          "range": "8284-8464",
          "rangeStart": 8284,
          "rangeEnd": 8464,
          "markText": "自从有了这辆车，他的生活过得越来越起劲了。拉包月也好，拉散座也好，他天天用不着为“车份儿”着急，拉多少钱全是自己的。心里舒服，对人就更和气，买卖也就更顺心。拉了半年，他的希望更大了：照这样下去，干上二年，至多二年，他就又可以买辆车，一辆，两辆……他也可以开车厂子了！\n可是，希望多半落空，祥子的也非例外。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1731206892,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-11-10 10:48:12",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8284&rangeEnd=8464",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8284&rangeEnd=8464"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_4_8446-8464",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8446-8464",
      "markText": "可是，希望多半落空，祥子的也非例外。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8446&rangeEnd=8464",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8446&rangeEnd=8464"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_7_6051-6131",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6051-6131",
      "markText": "祥子早就有点后悔，一听这个，更难过了。可是，继而一想，把三只活活的牲口卖给汤锅去挨刀，有点缺德；他和骆驼都是逃出来的，就都该活着。什么也没说，他心中平静了下去。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6051&rangeEnd=6131",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6051&rangeEnd=6131"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_18_2723-2799",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2723-2799",
      "markText": "她也是既旧又新的一个什么奇怪的东西，是姑娘，也是娘们；像女的，又像男的；像人，又像什么凶恶的走兽！这个走兽，穿着红袄，已经捉到他，还预备着细细的收拾他。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2723&rangeEnd=2799",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2723&rangeEnd=2799"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_13_1458-1484",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1458-1484",
      "markText": "毛病似乎是在他太老实，老实就必定吃亏，没有情理可讲！",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1458&rangeEnd=1484",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1458&rangeEnd=1484"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_23_1788-1811",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1788-1811",
      "markText": "人间的真话本来不多，一个女子的脸红胜过一大片话",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1788&rangeEnd=1811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1788&rangeEnd=1811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_22_1665-1742",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "1665-1742",
      "markText": "不久他又忍不下去了，想马上起来，还得去苦奔；道路是死的，人心是活的，在入棺材以前总是不断的希望着。可是，他立不起来。只好无聊的，乞怜的，要向虎妞说几句话：",
      "totalCount": 22,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1665&rangeEnd=1742",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1665&rangeEnd=1742"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_13_1542-1616",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1542-1616",
      "markText": "平日，他觉得自己是头顶着天，脚踩着地，无牵无挂的一条好汉。现在，他才明白过来，悔悟过来，人是不能独自活着的。特别是对那些同行的，现在都似乎有点可爱。",
      "totalCount": 20,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1542&rangeEnd=1616",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32da07163959366ce91b?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1542&rangeEnd=1616"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303571_21_7274-7324",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "7274-7324",
      "markText": "雨下给富人，也下给穷人；下给义人，也下给不义的人。其实，雨并不公道，因为下落在一个没有公道的世界上。",
      "totalCount": 20,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303571&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7274&rangeEnd=7324",
